</li><li> Bottles of Poison in <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/Faxanadu" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/Faxanadu">Faxanadu</a></em> are yellowish, as opposed to the more pink-colored Red Potions.
